# Input

```scss
/* http://tabatkins.github.io/specs/css-apply-rule/#defining */

:root {
  --toolbar-theme: {
    background-color: hsl(120, 70%, 95%);
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 1px solid var(--theme-color late);
  };
  --toolbar-title-theme: {
    color: green;
  };
}

:root {
  --without-semi: {color:red;}
}

:root {
  --like-a-apply-rule: {
  color:red;} /* no semi here*/
  --another-prop: blue;
}

:root {
  --like-a-apply-rule: {
  color:red;} /* no semi here*/
  --another-one-like-a-apply-rule: {
    color:red;
  };
}

```


